a\x09\x09\x09\x09absolute positioning for sub-classes */\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09position: relative;\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09padding-top: 1em;\x0a                display: flex;\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09flex-wrap: wrap;\x0a\x09\x09\x09}\x0a\x09\x09\x09.content-column-left {\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09/* Value for IE/Win; will be overwritten for other browsers */\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09width: 47%;\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09padding: 15px 30px;\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09margin-right: 30px;\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09padding-bottom: 2em;\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09margin-bottom: 1em;\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09flex: 1;\x0a\x09\x09\x09}\x0a\x09\x09\x09.content-column-left hr {\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09display: none;\x0a\x09\x09\x09}\x0a\x09\x09\x09.content-column-right {\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09/* Values for IE/Win; will be overwritten for other browsers */\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09width: 47%;\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09padding: 15px 30px;\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09padding-bottom: 2em;\x0a                margin-right: 30px;\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09margin-bottom: 1em;\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09flex: 1;\x0a\x09\x09\x09}\x0a\x09\x09\x09.content-columns>.content-column-left, .content-columns>.content-column-right {\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09/* Non-IE/Win */\x0a                border: 1px solid #d2d2d2;\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09border-radius: 3px;\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09box-sizing: border-box;\x0a\x09\x09\x09}\x0a\x09\x09\x09.logos {\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09text-align: left;\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09margin-top: 2em;\x0a\x09\x09\x09}\x0a            .logos a img {\x0a                padding-right: 1.5em;\x0a                margin-right: 1.5em;\x0a                border-right: 1px solid #d2d2d2;\x0a            }\x0a\x09\x09\x09img {\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09border: 2px solid #fff;\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09padding: 2px;\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09margin: 2px;\x0a\x09\x09\x09}\x0a\x09\x09\x09a:hover img {\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09border: 2px solid #f50;\x0a\x09\x09\x09}\x0a\x09\x09\x09.footer {\x0a\x09\x09\x09    font-size: xx-small;\x0a                padding: 0 10em;\x0a\x09\x09\x09    padding-bottom: 5em;\x0a\x09\x09\x09}\x0a\x0a            /* Responsive layout */\x0a            @media (max-width: 800px) {\x0a                .content-column-right, .content-column-left {\x0a                flex: 100%;\x0a                }\x0a            }\x0a\x09\x09\x09/*]]>*/\x0a\x09\x09</style>\x0a\x09</head>\x0a\x0a\x09<body>\x0a\x09\x09<h1>\x0a            <img src="system_noindex_logo.png" alt="AlmaLinux Logo" /><br />\x0a            Web Server <strong>Test Page</strong>\x0a        </h1>\x0a\x0a\x09\x09<div class="content">\x0a\x09\x09\x09<div class="content-middle">\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09<p>This page is used to test the proper operation of the HTTP server after it has been installed. If you can read this page, it means that the HTTP server installed at this site is working properly.</p>\x0a\x09\x09\x09</div>\x0a\x09\x09\x09<hr />\x0a\x0a\x09\x09\x09<div class="content-columns">\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09<div class="content-column-left">\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09<h2>If you are a member of the general public:</h2>\x0a\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09<p>The fact that you are seeing this page indicates that the website you just visited is either experiencing problems, or is undergoing routine maintenance.</p>\x0a\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09<p>If you would like to let the administrators of this website know that you've seen this page instead of the page you expected, you should send them e-mail. In general, mail sent to the name "webmaster" and directed to the website's domain should reach the appropriate person.</p>\x0a\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09<p>For example, if you experienced problems while visiting www.example.com, you should send e-mail to "webmaster@example.com".</p>\x0a\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09<p>For information on AlmaLinux, please visit the <a href="https://almalinux.org">AlmaLinux website</a>. The documentation for AlmaLinux is <a href="https://wiki.almalinux.org">available in AlmaLinux wiki</a>.</p>\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09<hr />\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09</div>\x0a\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09<div class="content-column-right">\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09<h2>If you are the website administrator:</h2>\x0a\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09<p>You may now add content to the webroot directory. Note\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09that until you do so, people visiting your website will see\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09this page, and not your content.</p>\x0a\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09<p>For systems using the Apache HTTP Server:\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09You may now add content to the directory <tt>/var/www/html/</tt>. Note that until you do so, people visiting your website will see this page, and not your content. To prevent this page from ever being used, follow the instructions in the file <tt>/etc/httpd/conf.d/welcome.conf</tt>.</p>\x0a\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09<p>For systems using NGINX:\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09You should now put your content in a location of your\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09choice and edit the <code>root</code> configuration directive\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09in the <strong>nginx</strong> configuration file\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09<code>/etc/nginx/nginx.conf</code>.</p>\x0a\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09<div class="logos">\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09<a href="https://almalinux.org"><img src= "/icons/poweredby.png" alt="[ Powered by AlmaLinux ]" /></a>\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09<img src= "poweredby.png" alt="[ Powered by AlmaLinux ]" />\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09\x09</div>\x0a\x09\x09\x09\x09</div>\x0a\x09\x09\x09</div>\x0a\x09\x09</div>\x0a\x09<div class="footer">\x0a\x09\x09<a href="https://apache.org">Apache&trade;</a> is a registered trademark of <a href="https://apache.org">the Apache Software Foundation</a> in the United States and/or other countries.\x0a        <br />\x0a\x09\x09<a href="https://nginx.com">NGINX&trade;</a> is a registered trademark of <a href="https://www.f5.com">F5 Networks, Inc.</a>.\x0a\x09</div>\x0a\x09</body>\x0a</html>\x0a

